{"tid":790903,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Note 9  說好的Water-Carbon Cooling系統呢？","createTime":"2018-08-23T11:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T08:11:39.000Z","uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc89abe11beb10a8faf70fcc54822fbbbc94e2e","tid":790903,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"Samsung 下半年旗艦 Galaxy Note 9 已經發佈了一段時間，早前已被知名「測試員」JerryRigEverything 作暴力測試，結果還算不俗。而且早前更有消息指銷情比 Galaxy S9 系列理想，相信 Samsung 都感到安慰。<br />\r\n不過原來 JerryRigEverything 對 Galaxy Note 9 進行暴力測試後，也把這部電話進行解體。而在解體後發現之前 Samsung 表示為 Galaxy Note 9 加入的「碳加水」散熱系統竟然找不到！<br />\r\n根據發放這個資料的成員 Zack Nelson 表示，解拆後可以看到 Galaxy Note 9 的散熱管尺寸比 Galaxy Note 8 明顯地大，跟 Razer 專為打遊戲而設計的智能電話相似，而散熱管上也有一塊很大的銅片用以散熱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n不過將扁平的散熱管道切開後，居然找不半點液體，而且也找不到任何屬於碳性的材料！液體有機會揮發掉，但碳性材料跑到哪兒去？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n相信只有 Samsung 才能提供得到答案了。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/22/fN20ik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2FfN20ik.jpg&h=f31c152e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5792af358cc706b06e4ebdcdcf988dfa339c789","tid":790903,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a7d2535dc9ab2b94f67a9953be40f1ff22d4666","tid":790903,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"吹水 Carbon Cooling <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔信咁大間會做假囉"},{"pid":"72cd30d0ba625e42f9ea827ad7f8b32dddf4e30b","tid":790903,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"就算有應該都唔會幫助，只係Gimmick，不過如果冇，note 9就收皮"},{"pid":"ce8b5812139d39b52e2b3e56396d91f5fa3d5e71","tid":790903,"uid":109383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72cd30d0ba625e42f9ea827ad7f8b32dddf4e30b","tid":790903,"uid":164092,"like